data.description: Welcome to the well established neighborhood of Visalia Glenara Rancho built in 1963 is a definite must see! This home sitting on 12,800 Lot has 3 bedrooms plus bonus room for piano, office or craft room, 2 Bath and 2 car garage. Home features a dining area equipped with fireplace and landscaping for very little care. Get ready for those hot summer days as you jump or slide into the sparkling and refreshing swimming pool! All appliances with no value and no warranty will be staying with property (dishwasher is inoperable). This Home is in a well-established part of Visalia with only a short drive to shopping center, restaurants, grocery stores, a community park, El Diamante School district and more! Contact your Real Estate Agent for a personal showing!
